},{"pid":"4fca245856e87a80dffc65172681f00242f2aec7","tid":262424,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T08:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就算有咩仇口都好<br />\n正常3個人黎計一定會勸阻大家,分析利弊<br />\n3個人一齊做9死者呢點認真奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似話死者係個War Game圈子出名握錢<br />\n唔排除金錢糾紛比人圍毆致死</blockquote><br />\n金錢糾紛最多都係執佢一劑教訓下佢<br />\n而家帶埋刀去攻擊死者,直頭係謀殺</blockquote><br />\n好多殺人都係火姐眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ef478cc649e7490cf800651e986be7d031e735","tid":262424,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就算有咩仇口都好<br />\n正常3個人黎計一定會勸阻大家,分析利弊<br />\n3個人一齊做9死者呢點認真奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好大仇口</blockquote><br />\n應該誤殺？如果係有仇口，即係有預謀，但係係人都知係果3條友約出黎，同埋咁樣處理屍體法，有上下連登都知要點處理啦，唔會真係咁蠢呀</blockquote><br />\n誘騙上山，唔係誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c30c3dad3a2ec207557fad04d13b87f0036c48","tid":262424,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T08:59:30.000Z","msg":"咁狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ded750e1197305d7464e0d797b37f41bbb1dca8","tid":262424,"uid":28358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"三五成群 2017版"},{"pid":"b429d5da2890a3155bc199e2b99ead183e6acf47","tid":262424,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就算有咩仇口都好<br />\n正常3個人黎計一定會勸阻大家,分析利弊<br />\n3個人一齊做9死者呢點認真奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好大仇口</blockquote><br />\n應該誤殺？如果係有仇口，即係有預謀，但係係人都知係果3條友約出黎，同埋咁樣處理屍體法，有上下連登都知要點處理啦，唔會真係咁蠢呀</blockquote><br />\n誘騙上山，唔係誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken